To protect nature, you can follow several actionable steps: reduce, reuse, and recycle to conserve resources and minimize waste; save energy at home and consider switching to renewable energy sources; walk, bike, or use public transport to reduce carbon emissions; consume less and choose reusable items over single-use products; and support local ecosystems by visiting green spaces and reducing meat consumption. Additionally, volunteering for conservation efforts and staying informed about environmental issues can also contribute to protecting our planet.